Node.Description: Go to Inventory management > Journal entries > Item counting > Counting.
In the Name field, enter or select a value.
In the list, click the link in the selected row.
Select No in the Warehouse field.
Select Yes in the Warehouse field.
Select No in the Inventory status field.
Select Yes in the Inventory status field.
Select No in the Location field.
Select Yes in the Location field.
In the list, mark the selected row.
In the Item number field, type a value.
In the Warehouse field, type a value.
In the Location field, type a value.
In the Quantity field, enter a number.
